data.description: Here's your chance to live in "The Lakes"!  This 4 br 4 ba 2 story home is a short walk from the beach, trail system, & East Lake Park.  Are you a car enthusiast?  The 3 stall garage is extra deep, insulated, heated, wired for EV charging, & it has a 2 car lift that stays!  The main level boasts a front office/library that could be used as a formal dining rm.  The living rm dining area, & large kitchen with center island are an open floor plan w/large windows for abundant natural light.  The composite deck overlooks the big, beautiful fenced back yard with its many fruit trees.  Convenient main flr laundry & a 1/2 bath. Upstairs you will find the primary bedroom suite featuring a private bath with jetted tub & separate shower.  Two more bedrooms & another full bath complete this level.  Downstairs features an office/craft room with built in countertop & cabinetry.  The family rm walks out to the backyard!  A 3/4 bath & 4th bedroom complete this level.  This could be your next home!
